item.title: How do you move deltascape shops?
item.dc:creator: @grimreaper61 grimreaper61
item.description:
@grimreaper61 wrote:

all delta servers come with a command called ::mypos. Go to where you want to place your shop and do ::mypos and you will find the coords you need
